The paper discusses the challenges and requirements of data mining on large datasets, specifically in the field of astronomy. This suggests that the paper could belong to the database (cs.DB), information retrieval (cs.IR), distributed computing (cs.DC), machine learning (cs.DL), or social and information networks (cs.SI) sub-categories. However, given the focus on data archiving and analysis, as well as the mention of database tools and data mining, cs.DB is the most likely sub-category.
